<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Living InnBlock | Modular Display Case Product Page</title>
  <meta name="description" content="A modern modular display case room for figures, designed to stack into an apartment-style InnBlock tower with lighting, panels, and connector rails.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="product">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Living InnBlock | Modular Display Case Room">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Stackable apartment-style display rooms for figures and collectibles.">
  <meta property="og:image" content="images/social-preview.png">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Living InnBlock | Modular Display Case Room">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Stackable apartment-style display rooms for figures and collectibles.">
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="images/social-preview.png">
  <link rel="icon" href="images/innblock-mark.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <script defer src="script.js"></script>
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Product",
    "name": "Living InnBlock",
    "description": "A modular display case room for figures, designed to stack into an apartment-style InnBlock tower.",
    "brand": { "@type": "Brand", "name": "INNBLOCK" },
    "image": "images/social-preview.png",
    "sku": "INN-LIV-WAL-01",
    "offers": {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "priceCurrency": "USD",
      "price": "1490.00",
      "availability": "https://schema.org/InStock"
    },
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.9",
      "reviewCount": "128"
    }
  }
  </script>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <a class="brand" href="#top" aria-label="INNBLOCK product page">
      <img src="images/innblock-mark.svg" alt="" width="32" height="32">
      <span>INNBLOCK</span>
    </a>

    <nav class="primary-nav" aria-label="Primary navigation">
      <a href="#stack-system">New Rooms</a>
      <a href="#included">Kits</a>
      <a href="#included">Accessories</a>
      <a href="#room-fit">Characters</a>
      <a href="#shipping">Pickup</a>
      <a href="#specs">About</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="header-actions">
      <button class="icon-button" type="button" aria-label="Search">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m21 21-4.35-4.35m2.1-5.4a7.5 7.5 0 1 1-15 0 7.5 7.5 0 0 1 15 0Z"></path></svg>
      </button>
      <button class="icon-button cart-button" type="button" aria-label="Cart">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.3 6h14.2l-1.7 8.4a2 2 0 0 1-2 1.6H8.3a2 2 0 0 1-2-1.7L4.9 3H2.8"></path><path d="M8.5 21a1.2 1.2 0 1 0 0-2.4 1.2 1.2 0 0 0 0 2.4Zm8.7 0a1.2 1.2 0 1 0 0-2.4 1.2 1.2 0 0 0 0 2.4Z"></path></svg>
        <span id="cartCount">2</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="top" class="product-page">
    <section class="product-shell" aria-labelledby="productTitle">
      <aside class="gallery-rail" aria-label="Product image gallery">
        <button class="thumb is-active" type="button" data-floor="4" data-kicker="Stack overview" data-title="Four-room apartment stack" data-copy="A complete InnBlock tower staged against a city apartment window." data-image="images/room-overview.jpg" aria-label="View stacked product overview">
          <img src="images/room-overview.jpg" alt="Full InnBlock apartment-style display stack">
        </button>
        <button class="thumb" type="button" data-floor="4" data-kicker="Floor 4" data-title="Living display room" data-copy="A warm display room with sofa, media wall, shelf rail, and LED ceiling wash." data-image="images/room-living.jpg" aria-label="View living room module">
          <img src="images/room-living.jpg" alt="Living room display module closeup">
        </button>
        <button class="thumb" type="button" data-floor="3" data-kicker="Floor 3" data-title="Studio and pose room" data-copy="Open space for taller figures, bikes, props, and flexible shelf staging." data-image="images/room-lounge.jpg" aria-label="View studio room module">
          <img src="images/room-lounge.jpg" alt="Studio display module closeup">
        </button>
        <button class="thumb" type="button" data-floor="2" data-kicker="Floor 2" data-title="Kitchen scene module" data-copy="A detailed everyday-room backdrop for slice-of-life figure photography." data-image="images/room-kitchen.jpg" aria-label="View kitchen room module">
          <img src="images/room-kitchen.jpg" alt="Kitchen display module closeup">
        </button>
        <button class="thumb" type="button" data-floor="1" data-kicker="Floor 1" data-title="Storage and accessory floor" data-copy="Use the bottom module for accessories, risers, spare hands, weapons, boxes, and diorama tools." data-image="images/room-storage.jpg" aria-label="View storage module">
          <img src="images/room-storage.jpg" alt="Storage display module closeup">
        </button>
        <button class="thumb" type="button" data-floor="spec" data-kicker="Scale guide" data-title="Module footprint" data-copy="A clean dimension reference for planning shelves, desks, and multi-room stacks." data-image="images/dimensions.svg" aria-label="View module dimensions">
          <img src="images/dimensions.svg" alt="InnBlock module dimension drawing">
        </button>
      </aside>

      <section class="visual-stage" aria-label="Stacked apartment product preview">
        <div class="city-scene">
          <p class="scene-label">Apartment-city display preview</p>
          <img class="tower-image" src="images/hero-stack.png" alt="Four modular InnBlock display rooms stacked into one apartment-style tower">
          <div class="focus-card" aria-live="polite">
            <img id="focusImage" src="images/room-overview.jpg" alt="Selected InnBlock preview">
            <div>
              <span id="focusKicker">Stack overview</span>
              <strong id="focusTitle">Four-room apartment stack</strong>
              <p id="focusCopy">A complete InnBlock tower staged against a city apartment window.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="elevator-control" aria-label="Elevator scroll control">
          <button class="elevator-arrow" type="button" data-scroll-target="top" aria-label="Scroll to top">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 14 6-6 6 6"></path></svg>
          </button>
          <div class="elevator-track" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="elevator-glow"></span>
            <span class="elevator-progress"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="floor-buttons" aria-label="Jump to product floors">
            <button class="floor-button is-active" type="button" data-floor="4">4</button>
            <button class="floor-button" type="button" data-floor="3">3</button>
            <button class="floor-button" type="button" data-floor="2">2</button>
            <button class="floor-button" type="button" data-floor="1">1</button>
          </div>
          <button class="elevator-arrow" type="button" data-scroll-target="details" aria-label="Scroll to floor details">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 10 6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
          </button>
        </div>
      </section>

      <aside class="product-info">
        <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <a href="#top">Rooms</a>
          <span>/</span>
          <a href="#stack-system">Living</a>
          <span>/</span>
          <span>Living InnBlock</span>
        </nav>

        <p class="eyebrow">Modular display room</p>
        <h1 id="productTitle">Living InnBlock</h1>

        <div class="price-review-row">
          <strong>$1,490.00</strong>
          <span class="stars" aria-label="Rated 4.9 out of 5">★★★★★</span>
          <span>4.9 (128 reviews)</span>
        </div>

        <p class="product-summary">A city-apartment display room for figures and collectibles. Stack it with other InnBlock rooms to build a vertical apartment-style showcase instead of a standard shelf row.</p>

        <div class="feature-grid" aria-label="Room features">
          <div>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 18h6m-5 3h4m-2-19a7 7 0 0 0-4 12.7V16h8v-1.3A7 7 0 0 0 12 2Z"></path></svg>
            <span>Premium LED lighting</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3 4 7v7c0 4.1 3.4 6.5 8 8 4.6-1.5 8-3.9 8-8V7l-8-4Z"></path><path d="m9 12 2 2 4-5"></path></svg>
            <span>Dust-resistant front-ready frame</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m12 3 9 5-9 5-9-5 9-5Z"></path><path d="m3 13 9 5 9-5"></path><path d="m3 18 9 5 9-5"></path></svg>
            <span>Modular and stackable</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8 8h8v8H8z"></path><path d="m3 3 18 18M16 3h5v5M3 16v5h5"></path></svg>
            <span>Hidden connector rail</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <section class="option-group" aria-labelledby="finishTitle">
          <div class="group-head">
            <h2 id="finishTitle">Finish</h2>
            <span id="selectedFinish">Walnut</span>
          </div>
          <div class="finish-options" role="radiogroup" aria-label="Choose finish">
            <button class="finish" type="button" role="radio" aria-checked="false" data-finish="Oak"><span class="swatch oak"></span><span>Oak</span></button>
            <button class="finish is-active" type="button" role="radio" aria-checked="true" data-finish="Walnut"><span class="swatch walnut"></span><span>Walnut</span></button>
            <button class="finish" type="button" role="radio" aria-checked="false" data-finish="Graphite"><span class="swatch graphite"></span><span>Graphite</span></button>
            <button class="finish" type="button" role="radio" aria-checked="false" data-finish="White"><span class="swatch white"></span><span>White</span></button>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="included" class="option-group" aria-labelledby="includedTitle">
          <div class="group-head">
            <h2 id="includedTitle">Included</h2>
            <span>Core kit</span>
          </div>
          <div class="included-grid">
            <article><span class="part-icon wall"></span><strong>Wall panels</strong><em>x4</em></article>
            <article><span class="part-icon floor"></span><strong>Floor panel</strong><em>x1</em></article>
            <article><span class="part-icon ceiling"></span><strong>Ceiling panel</strong><em>x1</em></article>
            <article><span class="part-icon led"></span><strong>LED strips</strong><em>x2</em></article>
            <article><span class="part-icon connector"></span><strong>Connectors</strong><em>x8</em></article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="option-group" aria-labelledby="addonTitle">
          <div class="group-head">
            <h2 id="addonTitle">Add-ons</h2>
            <span>Optional</span>
          </div>
          <div class="addon-list">
            <button class="addon" type="button" aria-pressed="false" data-addon="Display Shelf Pack">
              <span class="addon-thumb shelf"></span>
              <span><strong>Display Shelf Pack</strong><em>$49.00</em></span>
              <b>+</b>
            </button>
            <button class="addon" type="button" aria-pressed="false" data-addon="Figure Riser Set">
              <span class="addon-thumb riser"></span>
              <span><strong>Figure Riser Set</strong><em>$29.00</em></span>
              <b>+</b>
            </button>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="purchase-row">
          <div class="quantity-control" aria-label="Quantity selector">
            <button type="button" data-qty="decrease" aria-label="Decrease quantity">−</button>
            <output id="quantityValue" aria-live="polite">1</output>
            <button type="button" data-qty="increase" aria-label="Increase quantity">+</button>
          </div>
          <button class="add-to-cart" type="button" id="addToCart">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.3 6h14.2l-1.7 8.4a2 2 0 0 1-2 1.6H8.3a2 2 0 0 1-2-1.7L4.9 3H2.8"></path><path d="M8.5 21a1.2 1.2 0 1 0 0-2.4 1.2 1.2 0 0 0 0 2.4Zm8.7 0a1.2 1.2 0 1 0 0-2.4 1.2 1.2 0 0 0 0 2.4Z"></path></svg>
            Add to Cart
          </button>
          <button class="favorite" type="button" aria-label="Add to wishlist">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20.8 4.6a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.8 0L12 5.7l-1-1.1a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.8 7.8L12 21l8.8-8.6a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.8Z"></path></svg>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div id="shipping" class="shipping-notes">
          <p><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3 7h11v10H3zM14 11h4l3 3v3h-7z"></path><circle cx="7" cy="19" r="1.7"></circle><circle cx="18" cy="19" r="1.7"></circle></svg> Free shipping on orders over $150</p>
          <p><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M4 4h16v16H4z"></path><path d="M8 2v4m8-4v4M4 10h16"></path></svg> Ships in 3-5 business days</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <section class="benefit-strip" aria-label="Product benefits">
      <article>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m12 3 9 5-9 5-9-5 9-5Z"></path><path d="m3 13 9 5 9-5"></path></svg>
        <div><strong>Apartment stack</strong><span>Build upward instead of spreading across a shelf.</span></div>
      </article>
      <article>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5v14"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"></circle></svg>
        <div><strong>Made for collectors</strong><span>Designed around figures, props, risers, and small scenes.</span></div>
      </article>
      <article>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 2v20M5 7h14M5 17h14"></path></svg>
        <div><strong>Reconfigurable</strong><span>Swap floors, finishes, and display accessories.</span></div>
      </article>
      <article>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 3 4 7v7c0 4.1 3.4 6.5 8 8 4.6-1.5 8-3.9 8-8V7l-8-4Z"></path></svg>
        <div><strong>Stable connectors</strong><span>Interlocking rails keep the tower aligned.</span></div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section id="stack-system" class="details-section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <p class="eyebrow">Stack system</p>
        <h2>One product page, one vertical apartment.</h2>
        <p>Each floor is treated like a display room, but the product image stays stacked so the page always reads as a single InnBlock apartment tower.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="floor-grid">
        <article id="floor-4" class="floor-card" data-floor-section="4">
          <img src="images/room-living.jpg" alt="Living InnBlock floor closeup">
          <div><span>Floor 4</span><h3>Living display room</h3><p>Use the main floor for hero figures, seated poses, media props, and warm room lighting.</p></div>
        </article>
        <article id="floor-3" class="floor-card" data-floor-section="3">
          <img src="images/room-lounge.jpg" alt="Studio floor closeup">
          <div><span>Floor 3</span><h3>Studio and pose room</h3><p>Extra vertical clearance for taller figures, bikes, training props, and rotating scene setups.</p></div>
        </article>
        <article id="floor-2" class="floor-card" data-floor-section="2">
          <img src="images/room-kitchen.jpg" alt="Kitchen floor closeup">
          <div><span>Floor 2</span><h3>Kitchen scene room</h3><p>A detailed room backdrop that makes the product feel lived-in without turning the page into a storybook scene.</p></div>
        </article>
        <article id="floor-1" class="floor-card" data-floor-section="1">
          <img src="images/room-storage.jpg" alt="Storage floor closeup">
          <div><span>Floor 1</span><h3>Storage and accessory floor</h3><p>Keep accessories visible and organized while still making the tower look like a complete apartment block.</p></div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="specs" class="spec-section">
      <div class="spec-copy">
        <p class="eyebrow">Dimensions and fit</p>
        <h2>Built for clean display, not oversized scenery.</h2>
        <p>InnBlock rooms use a restrained footprint so the images support the purchase decision instead of overpowering the product page.</p>
        <dl class="spec-list">
          <div><dt>Prototype module size</dt><dd>15.8 in W x 15.7 in H x 12.0 in D</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Recommended use</dt><dd>Figures, miniatures, props, risers, and collectible accessories</dd></div>
          <div><dt>Stacking method</dt><dd>Interlocking side rails with concealed connector points</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
      <div class="dimension-card">
        <img src="images/dimensions.svg" alt="InnBlock modular display room dimension diagram">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="room-fit" class="room-fit-section">
      <div class="section-heading compact">
        <p class="eyebrow">Collector use</p>
        <h2>Room scenes for figures, not full-size furniture shopping.</h2>
        <p>The product page uses image-based modules, city lighting, and a restrained interface so the case remains the product.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <div class="toast" id="toast" role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>
</body>
</html>
